short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Convert between UTC milliseconds since epoch and UTC quarter.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you ever need to know what quarter an epoch millisecond timestamp falls in, this extension is for you!

Example conversion from millis to quarter:
1546545520683 (~Jan 3, 2019 11:59AM) -> 2019Q1

You can also convert from quarter to epoch millisecond timestamp. The converter will return the first millisecond in the given quarter.

Example conversion from quarter to millis:
2019Q1 -> 1546300800000 (Jan 1, 2019, 12:00AM)
